<section id="H9AC36434CF404954B0C9DFF65CE7E933" section-type="section-one"><enum>1.</enum><header>Short title</header><text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the <quote><short-title>Refinancing Relief for Veterans Act</short-title></quote>.</text></section> <section id="H14C2BCF7FCBC48DC924868BEE3D4C43A"><enum>2.</enum><header>Adjustment of fees for interest rate reduction refinancing housing loans guaranteed insured, or made by the Secretary of Veterans Affairs</header><text display-inline="no-display-inline">The loan fee table in section 3729(b)(2) of title 38, United States Code, is amended by striking the row in subparagraph (E) (relating to interest rate reduction refinancing loans) and inserting the following:</text> 
